  <p class="gd-byline" style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:12.5px;letter-spacing:.05em;color:var(--blue-soft);opacity:.9;margin:16px 0 0">By <a href="/about" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px">Vegard Knudsen</a> · Founder, Heliski Travel · Updated 5 May 2026</p>
  <p class="gd-lede">When the Northern Alps go green, the Andes go white. Chile and Argentina are the big-terrain way to keep skiing through summer — and they pair beautifully with our Iceland <a href="/packages">packages</a>. Here is the honest guide, and how it complements a Viking week in <a href="/iceland">Iceland</a>.</p>
